snippet.textDisplay: The song "Allah Megh De Pani De Chhaya Dere Tui" sung by Coke Studio Bangla Season 01 was sung by Mamtaz Apa and Mizan Bhai, two arrogant and legendary musicians of Bangladesh. There was another person involved who I may not know but I became a fan of him. The musicians have played their instruments in a wonderful way. In a word, Shayan Chowdhury Arnob the music director of Coke Studio Bangla has performed a song that makes Bangladesh proud.
